{"tid":2015563,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"！！黃色經濟圈第一個家務助理正式上線！！","createTime":"2020-05-13T18:32:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T17:05:51.000Z","uid":264783,"like":51,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"7c02c77d993f17b4a3a9132ca01c141de934da80","tid":2015563,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T18:32:08.000Z","msg":"因為咁啱媽咪呢排無嘢做，就決定重拾舊對做家務助理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n伯母差唔多20年前嚟香港，之前後就考咗個ERB家務助理，再斷斷續續上人屋企幫手做吓家務、賺下錢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實原本無諗住喺連登開po叫人幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只係發現隔離po話香港無黃色家務助理就諗住俾大家多個選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以follow IG: cleaner_hk<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/cleaner__hk?igshid=e5pd3stb0ntc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fcleaner__hk%3Figshid%3De5pd3stb0ntc&d=xUEPa7L8eIFrsai6sDUjHK0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=49cee541\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/cleaner__hk?igshid=e5pd3stb0ntc</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然老母會得閒幫襯下黃色經濟圈同埋屌下中國共產黨 但作為仔女都覺得佢可以更黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 歡迎大家有緣見到佢嘅時候 再陰啲陰啲教育下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7wmPsZ1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7wmPsZ1.png&h=5c993e3c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"763880be5130af1a33f842c63c578c28c818544f","tid":2015563,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T18:32:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NkRzx1A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNkRzx1A.gif&h=65e3b426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">見到連鄺俊宇自己都保唔住，你仲相信「溫柔是最大的勇武嗎？」</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">取消功能組別 五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全民習武 唯一出路</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"bbd811bdb1e8dfc8f5032ed2685168eef8ee9d5e","tid":2015563,"uid":264783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T18:34:21.000Z","msg":"服務提供<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n✅窗戶清洗\t<br />\n室內窗戶及窗框清洗<br />\n室外窗戶清洗 (客戶須提供合適的輔助工具，如長手柄的工具)。<br />\n如服務員工認為有關工作嚴重危害其人身安全時，他們有權拒絕執行。<br />\n✅廚房清潔\t<br />\n清洗抽氣扇及抽油煙機表面<br />\n清潔煮食爐 / 雪櫃<br />\n清洗碗盤、烹調器皿、碗碟<br />\n✅浴室清洗\t<br />\n抽氣扇<br />\n座廁、浴缸、洗手盆刷洗<br />\n✅其他清潔\t<br />\n室內地板吸塵及拖地<br />\n洗燙衣服<br />\n更換床單及枕袋<br />\n抹傢具<br />\n清潔冷氣機隔塵網、風扇 (由於市面有各款風扇型號，建議先由客戶拆除，否則服務員工有權拒絕拆除清洗)<br />\n✅盤點及代購家居日常用品\t<br />\n替客戶盤點家居日常用品存量 (如：廁所用品、清潔用品、調味料等)，如有需要，可提供補購清單及代為購買<br />\n客戶亦可提供購物清單由服務員工代購。購物時間需視乎物品類別及數量，但會以就近快捷為原則 (購物時間計算於整段服務時間)<br />\n✅星期一至日，上午九時至下午七時, 至少三小時(可議)，地點屯門元朗天水圍(可議)<br />\n❇️十七年經驗，在2003年獲取專業家務助理員牌照，工作時可要求出示<br />\n✅90元一小時 明價實價 至少一星期一次"},{"pid":"d434cdf73a885ab2105378866355aeb055df3e5d","tid":2015563,"uid":178800,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T19:25:21.000Z","msg":"樓主,建議你可以同老母講,搵多D志同道合既同路人師奶<br />\n組成黃色家務助理連線<br />\n當然,我地手足客戶好高要求的,會留意各位會否有扮黃"},{"pid":"6a7a508d661662405d2aa48dfc15256e7fff2b65","tid":2015563,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T19:27:05.000Z","msg":"開拓新既經濟線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a715c9eb30dbeeb99092782232fbed7d54228aa","tid":2015563,"uid":106574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T19:30:05.000Z","msg":"有機會幫襯下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02db65b45000e0d37652faa64d93157f50bb10de","tid":2015563